"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"先在<https://app.sushi.com/swap> 兑换点USDT、USDC、DAI。\\n\\n1）打开 [https://app.hop.exchange](https://t.co/9jqZI5E6ec) ，选Polygon链。\\n\\n2）点Convert，将例如USDT转化为hUSDT。2.1个hUSDT即可。\\n\\n3）点击Pool，添加例如USDT和hUSDT流动性。大约2.1 USDT--2.1USD\\n\\n我添加了USDT-hUSDT、USDC-hUSDC、DAI-hDAI、MATIC-hDAI等流动性。\\n\\n注意事项：获得这个角色，账户里要有LP不能拿去STAKE。\\n\\n4）进入不和谐。\\n\\nDiscord:<https://discord.gg/PwCF88emV4> 找到#CollabLand-join，点击Collab.Land，点击Let's go!连钱包，得role。成功的标志是你在聊天的时候会发现你的账号名字变色了。\\n\\nHOP是一个跨链桥。平时有需要可以去交互。跨链桥也是埋伏空投的一个热点。\",\"timestamp\":1641213683,\"title\":\"HopProtocol提供LP获得Role 教程\"},\"digest\":\"85taVxXq_Kwt4dy1nZYlLx2KmJ8EVd8BlncAHxGq3r8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x0D16c0308B39E9576e8812d063008b6ACFD7353b\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"0Duo0AWKkVznoeilIkkI9UuyChllgugqRKjz3CWpF90\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Uw8xawqIhkv8oAflXfSKjctR65qnV6cE6XgZOCibmQM\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"-RXc8Y3CTDOfqzqGQvA0eSyQWOmtKS2ph4oAY5qRWuFVtIsJXgr5lm6S299pJccOp_BZxl8ghKi6nn7EHkvMuw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x07bccf7a70b07b5c0c5aed2ce48122bfe5870d87022f37af646979eca54ee743711959c21aa85b2c8335b084b595c557bca8fa2f390f3e5922efe344a3e7c8851c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"0Duo0AWKkVznoeilIkkI9UuyChllgugqRKjz3CWpF90\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Uw8xawqIhkv8oAflXfSKjctR65qnV6cE6XgZOCibmQM\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"85taVxXq_Kwt4dy1nZYlLx2KmJ8EVd8BlncAHxGq3r8\"}"